item.description:
Please come join us as we distribute literature in Farmington for Honey's important August 9th election.

We will be meeting in Farmington in the St. Peter Church parking lot at 9:00 to hand out walking lists and the literature.

Time: 9 - 12

Lunch will be provided afterwards.

Directions: Take Rt. 125 north from Barrington to the entrance to Spaulding Tpk. in Rochester and go north to Exit 15. Exit onto 11 West and go about 6 miles, through 4 traffic lights to the intersection of Rt. 11 and Rt. 75 - a Rite Aid will be on your right). Take that right onto Rt. 75 and go about 1/2 mile, cross over the Mad River bridge and take the left immediately after the bridge into the parking lot of St. Peter.
item.name: Lit Drop for Honey Puterbaugh in Farmington
